videos.headline: Ellis barrels in for Virginia TD
videos.description: Virginia RB Jordan Ellis rushes up the middle for a 1-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Benkert's TD extends Virginia lead
videos.description: Virginia QB Kurt Benkert completes a 34-yard touchdown pass to Andre Levrone in the second quarter.

videos.headline: Virginia pads lead with Benkert's 2nd passing TD
videos.description: Virginia QB Kurt Benkert completes a  17-yard touchdown pass to Olamide Zaccheaus.

videos.headline: Dowling hurdles defender for big gain
videos.description: Virginia WR Doni Dowling leaps over the cornerback to gain 26 yards.

videos.headline: McKee puts William & Mary on the board
videos.description: QB Tommy McKee rushes up the middle for a two-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Virginia's defense the difference maker
videos.description: Dave Weekley and Matt Chatham discuss the key factors on both sides of the ball in Virginia's 28-10 win.
